  "body": "/kind bug\r\n\r\n**What happened**:\r\n\r\nCurrently HPA code issues a GET request to API server every time it analyses pods to be scaled. This introduces significant latency and reduces HPA controller throughput.  \r\n\r\n**What you expected to happen**:\r\n\r\nUse informers local cache to reduce API server load and improve performance. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/5b355f5d408c80234b4016a84b4d7c8159db21d7/cmd/kube-controller-manager/app/autoscaling.go#L85\r\n\r\n**How to reproduce it (as minimally and precisely as possible)**:\r\n\r\nIt is happening every time HPA is used. \r\n\r\ncc: @DirectXMan12 @krzysztof-jastrzebski \r\n\r\n",
